======================================================================
TEST SUITE FOR PERSONAL INFORMATION MANAGER
======================================================================

--- TEST CASE 1: Standard Valid Inputs ---
Expected Behavior: Program accepts inputs on first try and outputs the profile.
• Favorite Food : Curry
• Favorite Color: Black

--- TEST CASE 2: Edge Case - Empty Input Handling ---
Expected Behavior: Program catches empty spaces, throws a red error sign (❌), and re-prompts.
• Favorite Food : [Press Enter key directly without typing]
• Favorite Food (Retry): Noodles
• Favorite Color: Green

--- TEST CASE 3: Edge Case - Trailing Spaces ---
Expected Behavior: Program strips out whitespace using string methods (.strip()) before formatting.
• Favorite Food : "   pizza   "
• Favorite Color: "  red  "
